  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ER02IR Action Dialogue GA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall objective of the action is to rebuild confidence in peacebuilding and widen the pool of civil society actors engaged in promoting peaceful resolution of the Georgian-Abkhaz and Georgian-South Ossetian conflicts.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The specific objectives are: &#xB7; To strengthen existing grassroots South Ossetian civil society and prepare the ground for confidence building, dialogue and public diplomacy; &#xB7; To foster people to people contacts through economic cooperation between small business / households in Abkhazia &amp; South Ossetia (e.g. between East/West Abkhazia; Georgians &amp; South Ossetians). &#xB7; To influence public dialogue and contribute analysis and new ideas on conflict-related subjects.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#xB7; Teachers, social workers or others in a position to do outreach to their communities in all districts of South Ossetia &#xB7; Small business people and farmers in Abkhazia &amp; South Ossetia &#xB7; Experts, analysts, the media, the local &#x2018;peacebuilding community&#x2019; in Georgia, Abkhazia, South Ossetia,</narrative>
  </description>
